data.description: What a location for this spacious family home, just outside the city limits of Hillsdale.  Nestled in a quiet neighborhood not far from the Country Club, Baw Beese Lake, or the conveniences of town.  Peaked cathedral ceilings welcome you in to the living room.  Formal dining area or eat in kitchen; the floor plan allows for flexibility in use of space.  3 bedrooms & 2 full baths upstairs. All of the rooms in this home are spacious and comfortable.  Full basement with potential to finish for more living area. Fenced area in the yard, 2 car attached garage. Appliances included.
